PageSpeed Insights
This preset will give you a dashboard with widgets containing your Lighthouse scores from your PageSpeed Insights checks.
PageSpeed Insights
Accessibility score
Will show you the Lighthouse score on accessibility from the last PageSpeed Insights check.
Performance score
Will show you the Lighthouse score on performance from the last PageSpeed Insights check.
Best Practices score
Will show you the Lighthouse score on best practices from the last PageSpeed Insights check.
PWA score
Will show you the Lighthouse score on PWA from the last PageSpeed Insights check.
SEO score
Will show you the Lighthouse score on SEO from the last PageSpeed Insights check.
History of Lighthouse scores
Will show you the Lighthouse scores of all categories from the PageSpeed Insights checks of the last month.
